"{\"uid\": \"thewrap.com-tom-cruise-paris-olympics-closing-ceremony\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Mission: Impossible\\\" star has attended several events at the 2024 summer games  The Paris Olympics are expected to close out the summer games with some star power from Tom Cruise, according to media reports.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 173, \"end\": 183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tom Cruise\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Cruise\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The \\\"Mission: Impossible\\\" star, who has been a spectator at several Olympic events so far, is poised to make an appearance at the closing ceremony on Aug. 11.\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Cruise is expected to employ some \\\"Mission: Impossible\\\" stunts as part of a \\\"major Hollywood production\\\" expected to take place at the ceremony, Deadline and TMZreported.\", \"from\": 373, \"to\": 543, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 456, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.5935525162697814e-12, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Appearances from Hollywood figures would be in line with plans for the ceremony, which will see Paris Mayor Anne Hidalgo pass the Olympic flag onto Los Angeles mayor Karen Bass ahead of the 2028 Summer Olympics.\", \"from\": 545, \"to\": 756, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 562, \"end\": 571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.5935525162697814e-12, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"