clude Zendaya, Nicole Kidman, Jessica Chastain, Shaun White and Nina Dobrev, Nick Jonas, Elizabeth Banks, Judd Apatow, Leslie Mann, Alan Cumming, Pharrell, Charlize Theron, John Legend and Chrissy Teigen, among others.\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1424, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1137, \"end\": 1146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999999984084, \"rank\": 1.5935525162697814e-12, \"text\": \"Hollywood\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cinema_of_the_United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1212, \"end\": 1219, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zendaya\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0312631215837952e-30, \"text\": \"Zendaya\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zendaya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zendaya\"}, {\"begin\": 1221, \"end\": 1234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8267047517311544e-40, \"text\": \"Nicole Kidman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nicole_Kidman\"}, {\"begin\": 1236, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Chastain\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7007840877044986e-34, \"text\": \"Jessica Chastain\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Chastain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jessica_Chastain\"}, {\"begin\": 1254, \"end\": 1265, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shaun White\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shaun_White\"}, {\"begin\": 1270, \"end\": 1281, \"