dia.org/resource/Charlize_Theron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2668752530883953e-41, \"text\": \"Charlize Theron\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlize_Theron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlize_Theron\"}, {\"begin\": 1379, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Legend\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Legend\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Legend\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Legend\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony also contained plenty of U.S. powerhouses, with both Lady Gaga andCeline Diontaking the Parisian stage.\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1550, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1500, \"end\": 1509, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As Dion sang \\u00c9dith Piaf's \\\"L'Hymne \\u00e0 l'amour,\\\" she performed publicly for the first time since she was diagnosed with \\\"stiff person syndrome,\\\" a rare neurological disease, in 2022.\", \"from\": 1551, \"to\": 1731, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1564, \"end\": 1574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"score\": 0.9999999997958184, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"\\u00c9dith Piaf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her performance was revered by many, including commentator Kelly Clarkson, who sounded teary as she reacted to the moment.\", \"from\": 1732, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1791, \"end\": 1805, \"title\": \"http://dbp